lead_paragraph: New York Mets pitcher Noah Syndergaard was amused when Kauffman Stadium's sound system played "American Woman" as he trotted out to the mound for the first inning.

headline.print_headline: Syndergaard, Mets Shut Out Royals Following Ring Ceremony
